<plot>Shy young Roland Wright deals with his tortured existance at home with his nagging parents in a tower block and at school with his bullies &amp; tyrannical teachers by withdrawing into a fantasy world where everyone he knows is transformed into hideous doubles. When he falls down a lift shaft this fantasy becomes reality, and Roland must recover a number of missing keys, overcome his enemies... and become "King of the Castle"!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?292598</url></doc>
